---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
import ContactGrid from "../components/ContactGrid.astro";
---

<MainLayout title="Contact">
  <div id="luxy">
    <div class="content" style="padding-top: 30vh;">
      <h1 class="title">Identity</h1>
      <article style="margin-bottom: 150px;">
        <p>Sanalog is preferably rendered as <code>Sanalog</code>. <br> <code>sanalog_</code> is also used for services that require an all-lowercase handle.</p>
        <p>This page lists some of them I use. It is not a request to follow or otherwise connect to me. The list is non-exhaustive. If you find me on other services, I don't use them often enough to warrant a mention, but you're welcome to interact with it, creep.</p>
        <p>You can <a href="mailto:me@sanalog.net" style="color:#000e;">[email: me (at) sanalog.net</a>]. For a faster reply, message me on Discord.</p>
      </article>
      <h1 class="title">Social</h1>
      <div class="contacts_grid">
        <ContactGrid
          link="https://twitter.com/sanalog_"
          service="Twitter"
          username="@sanalog_" />
        <ContactGrid
          link="https://www.instagram.com/sanalog_"
          service="Instagram"
          username="@sanalog_" />
        <ContactGrid
          link="https://discord.com/channels/@me/258172826039746561"
          service="Discord"
          username="sanalog" />
        <ContactGrid
          link="https://www.reddit.com/u/Sanalog"
          service="Reddit"
          username="u/Sanalog" />
        <ContactGrid
          link="https://github.com/itsSanalog"
          service="GitHub"
          username="@itsSanalog" />
        <ContactGrid
          link="https://www.linkedin.com/in/[redacted]"
          service="LinkedIn"
